prodNameC: 亞培IMx雌二醇檢驗試劑組
ingredientsDesc:
Reagent Pack
1. 1Bottle (6.5mL) Anti-Estradiol (Rabbit, polyclonal) Coated Microparticles in BIS-TRIS Buffer
2.1Bottle (10mL) Estrogen: Alkaline Phosphatase Conjugate in BIS-TRIS Buffer
3. 1Bottle (10mL) 4-Methylumbelliferyl Phosphate, 1.2mM, in AMP Buffer
4. 1Bottle (13mL) Buffer containing surfactant.
MODE 1 Calibrator
1 Bottle (4mL) MODE 1 Calibrator (C). Concentration: 250 p g/mL Estradiol in TRIS buffer with protein stabilizers.
Calibrators (A~F)
The six bottles (4mL each) of IMx Estradiol Calibrators contain Estradiol prepared in TRIS buffer with protein stabilizers. (conc. 0、50、250、750、1500、3000 pg/mL)
Controls (L、M、H)
The three bottles (8mL each) of IMx Estradiol Controls contain Estradiol prepared in TRIS buffer with protein stabilizers (conc. 150、500、1125 pg/mL)
Specimen Diluent
1 Bottle (10mL) of IMxEstradiol Specimen Diluent, humn serum.
applicantName: 美商亞培股份有限公司台灣分公司
applicantAddr: 台北市中山區民生東路三段49號5、6樓及51號5、6樓
efficacy: 微粒酵素免疫分析法，測試人類血清及血漿中的雌二醇。
